                     <interp inst="t17820515-50-off244" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing three silver tea-spoons, value 3 s. and a linen sheet, value 1 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17820515-50-victim461" type="victimName">
                     Robert 
                     Sharp
                  <interp inst="t17820515-50-victim461" type="surname" value="Sharp"></interp>
